#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>gzip</command> is a compression program"
msgstr "<command>gzip</command> je program za stiskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The gzip KIO worker is not directly usable, and is intended for use as a "
"filter. For example, the tar KIO worker can filter a file through the gzip "
"KIO worker, in order to display the contents of a <literal role=\"extension"
"\">tar.gz</literal> file directly in a &konqueror; window."
msgstr ""
"KIO worker za gzip ni neposredno uporaben, saj je mišljen za uporabo kot "
"filter. Tako lahko na primer KIO worker za tar datoteko filtrira skozi KIO "
"worker-ja za gzip, da prikaže vsebino datoteke <literal role=\"extension"
"\">tar.gz</literal> neposredno v oknu programa &konqueror;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you click on a file compressed with a <literal role=\"extension\">gz</"
"literal> extension in &konqueror;, this KIO worker is used to uncompress it "
"and display it as a normal (uncompressed) file."
msgstr ""
"Če v &konqueror;-ju kliknete na datoteko stisnjeno z <literal role="
"\"extension\">.gz</literal>, se ta KIO worker uporabi za razširjenje "
"datoteke in jo prikaže kot običajno (nestisnjeno) datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are a developer, and would like to use the gzip filter, you can find "
"documentation on using KIO workers at <ulink url=\"http://techbase.kde.org"
"\">http://techbase.kde.org</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Če ste razvijalec in bi želeli uporabiti gzip filter, lahko najdete "
"dokumentacijo o uporabi KIO worker-jev na <ulink url=\"http://developer.kde."
"org\">http://techbase.kde.org</ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the manual: <ulink url=\"man:/gzip\">gzip</ulink>."
msgstr "Oglejte si priročnik: <ulink url=\"man:/gzip\">gzip</ulink>."
